 Initial ns;result;buff
‚çù 1. Create the needed references
‚çù 2. Set global `DEVELOPMENT` depending on user decision (if not running in batch mode)
‚çù 3. Create two namespaces with (very little) content
‚çù 4. Create two Cider projects from those two namespaces
‚çù 5. Initialize both Cider projects as local Git repositories

 A‚ÜêAPLTreeUtils2
 F‚ÜêFilesAndDirs
 G‚ÜêAPLGit2‚Üê##.APLGit2

 :If ns.batchFlag
     ‚éïSE.APLGit2.‚éïEX'DEVELOPMENT'
 :Else
     ‚éïSE.APLGit2.DEVELOPMENT‚Üê1 CommTools.YesOrNo'Run code in ‚éïSE when a user command (rather than #.APLGit2) ?'
 :EndIf

 ‚àÜLINK_NOTIFY_WAS‚Üê‚éïSE.Link.NOTIFY
 ‚éïSE.Link.NOTIFY‚Üê0
 ‚àÜTempDir‚ÜêF.GetTempSubDir'Git_Tests'
 3 ‚éïMKDIR ‚àÜFolder1‚ÜêG.F.EnforceSlash ‚àÜTempDir,'/NoBlanks'
 3 ‚éïMKDIR ‚àÜFolder2‚ÜêG.F.EnforceSlash ‚àÜTempDir,'/Has Blanks'
 3 ‚éïMKDIR ‚àÜFolder3‚ÜêG.F.EnforceSlash ‚àÜTempDir,'/StagedAndUnTracked'

 'Proj_1'#.‚éïNS''
 #.Proj_1.(‚éïIO ‚éïML)‚Üê1
 #.Proj_1.‚éïFX‚Üë'r‚ÜêWhoAmI' 'r‚Üê''Proj_1'''
 (‚àÜFolder1,'/cider.config')‚éïNCOPY ##.CiderConfig.HOME,'/TestData/cider.config.1'
 result‚Üê‚éïSE.UCMD'Cider.CreateProject ',‚àÜFolder1,' #.Proj_1 -acceptConfig -noEdit -batch -ignoreUserExec'
 {}‚àÜInitialize ‚àÜFolder1
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello' 'r‚Üê''world''')‚éïNPUT ‚àÜFolder1,'/APLSource/help.aplf'
 ‚àÜFolder1 G.Add''
 buff‚Üê'Function added'G.Commit ‚àÜFolder1
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello' 'r‚Üê''World''')‚éïNPUT(‚àÜFolder1,'/APLSource/help.aplf')1
 ‚àÜFolder1 G.Add''

 'Proj_2'#.‚éïNS''
 #.Proj_2.(‚éïIO ‚éïML)‚Üê1
 #.Proj_2.‚éïFX‚Üë'r‚ÜêWhoAmI' 'r‚Üê''Proj_2'''
 (‚àÜFolder2,'/cider.config')‚éïNCOPY ##.CiderConfig.HOME,'/TestData/cider.config.2'
 result‚Üê‚éïSE.UCMD'Cider.CreateProject "',‚àÜFolder2,'" #.Proj_2 -acceptConfig -noEdit -batch -ignoreUserExec'
 {}‚àÜInitialize ‚àÜFolder2
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello2' 'r‚Üê''Galaxy''')‚éïNPUT ‚àÜFolder2,'/APLSource/help2.aplf'

 'Proj_3'#.‚éïNS''
 #.Proj_3.(‚éïIO ‚éïML)‚Üê1
 #.Proj_3.‚éïFX‚Üë'r‚ÜêWhoAmI' 'r‚Üê''Proj_3'''
 (‚àÜFolder3,'/cider.config')‚éïNCOPY ##.CiderConfig.HOME,'/TestData/cider.config.3'
 result‚Üê‚éïSE.UCMD'Cider.CreateProject "',‚àÜFolder3,'" #.Proj_3 -acceptConfig -noEdit -batch -ignoreUserExec'
 {}‚àÜInitialize ‚àÜFolder3
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello2' 'r‚Üê''Galaxy''')‚éïNPUT ‚àÜFolder3,'/APLSource/help2.aplf'
 {}‚àÜFolder3 G.U.RunGitCommand'add ',‚àÜFolder3,'/APLSource/help2.aplf'
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello3' 'r‚Üê''Virgo''')‚éïNPUT ‚àÜFolder3,'/APLSource/help3.aplf'
 {}‚àÜFolder3 G.U.RunGitCommand'add ',‚àÜFolder3,'/APLSource/help3.aplf'
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello3' 'r‚Üê''Virgo Cluster''')‚éïNPUT(‚àÜFolder3,'/APLSource/help3.aplf')1
 (‚äÇ'r‚ÜêHello4' 'r‚Üê''Universe''')‚éïNPUT ‚àÜFolder3,'/APLSource/help4.aplf'
 #.Proj_3.‚éïFX‚Üë'r‚ÜêWhoAmI' '‚çù Really!' 'r‚Üê''Proj_3'''
 {}#.Proj_3 ‚éïSE.Link.Add ‚éïSE.Link.GetFileName'#.Proj_3.WhoAmI'
‚çùDone
